Glimt,com,is,an,event,discovery,platform,Glimt,com,aggregates,event,data,from,multiple,sources,and,adds,geotag,to,all,events,in,Norway,Glimt,com,displays,events,via,lists,or,maps,Events,of,all,types,are,included,The,Glimt,com,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Glimt,com,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,events,retrieving,event,details,and,searching,for,events,by,keyword,location,and,type